text: Žirovnice () is a town in Pelhřimov District in the Vysočina Region of the Czech Republic. About 3,300 people live there. == Twin towns == Žirovnice is twinned with: * Grosshöchstetten, Switzerland * Trstená, Slovakia == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Towns in the Czech Republic Category:Vysočina Region
